OL,3,C"Deep concerns" - Guernsey charity
OL,4,Cwarns of growing homelessness
OL,6,FA Guernsey charity has reported a
OL,7,Fdramatic increase in referrals to help
OL,8,Fpeople who have found themselves
OL,9,Fhomeless so far this year.
OL,11,FAt Home in Guernsey says it has been
OL,12,Fin touch with 104 clients so far in
OL,13,F2026 - up from 125 across the whole of
OL,14,Flast year.
OL,16,FThe charity offers support to those
OL,17,Flooking for housing and raises
OL,18,Fawareness of a problem they say is
OL,19,Fgrowing on island.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
