OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1780600264
OL,3,C"Deep concerns" - Guernsey charity
OL,4,Cwarns of growing homelessness
OL,6,FMany of its new clients had been
OL,7,Frenting properties whose lets expired
OL,8,Fin late March.
OL,10,FNow, as lodging houses and hotels fill
OL,11,Fduring the summer months, they are
OL,12,Fleft searching for somewhere to stay.
OL,14,FOne of those clients is Tracey and she
OL,15,Fis based at St Julian's House, the
OL,16,Fonly emergency homeless shelter in
OL,17,FGuernsey.
OL,19,FTracey told ITV News her aim was to
OL,20,Fget a job and rent a flat, but she's
OL,21,Fstruggled.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
