FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1780600264
OL,3,C"Deep concerns" - Guernsey charity
OL,4,Cwarns of growing homelessness
OL,6,F"If we're here, it's not really
OL,7,Fpossible for us to better ourselves."
OL,9,F"We can't even really save up the
OL,10,Fmoney for a deposit".
OL,12,FOne thousand people are estimated to
OL,13,Fbe without housing in Guernsey, but
OL,14,Fthe specific circumstances vary. They
OL,15,Fare sleeping in cars, lodging houses,
OL,16,Fand hotels.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
