PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1780600264
OL,3,C"Deep concerns" - Guernsey charity
OL,4,Cwarns of growing homelessness
OL,6,FAt Home in Guernsey CEO Charlie Cox
OL,7,Fsaid they were surprised by the rise
OL,8,Fin clients and said the charity is
OL,9,Fdoing its best to help, but needed
OL,10,Fmore support.
OL,12,FThe charity also noted the increase in
OL,13,Fnumbers may be because more people are
OL,14,Faware of the services they offer.
OL,16,FCharlie Cox said that while the
OL,17,Fcharity are "delighted that people are
OL,18,Fcoming to us, it just demonstrates the
OL,19,Fneed to be doing more".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
