PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1780600264
OL,3,C"Deep concerns" - Guernsey charity
OL,4,Cwarns of growing homelessness
OL,6,FCaitlin Duquemin, a Support Worker at
OL,7,FAt Home in Guernsey, said that the
OL,8,Fcharity is "deeply concerned by the
OL,9,Frise in islanders coming to us in
OL,10,Fcrisis".
OL,12,FShe also said the number of people at
OL,13,Frisk of homelessness was "likely" to
OL,14,Fcontinue to grow.
OL,16,FAt Home in Guernsey takes referrals in
OL,17,Fperson and online through the
OL,18,F"Homelessness Notification Form" that
OL,19,Flaunched in November 2025.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
